#weather app

- The app can be used to search for weather data in any city
- Background images changes from day to night based on the time in the city. 
- Icon related the the weather (haze, snow, sunny, etc) changes as well.

https://codesbya.github.io/weather-app/
The site uses AccuWeather API to retrieve weather data.   
